<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 12:50:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加密行业在熊市中举办脱衣舞派对</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-09/crypto-industry-throws-lap-dance-party-in-middle-of-bear-market</link><description>周三晚上，人们排着几个街区的队，等待了几个小时才进入迈阿密的 E11even 俱乐部，几个男人兴奋地谈论着他们计划进入的膝上舞。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i79v8LGzeGTc/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-09/crypto-industry-throws-lap-dance-party-in-middle-of-bear-market</guid></item><item><title>贝莱德准备推出两只代币化货币市场基金</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-08/blackrock-readies-launch-of-two-tokenized-money-market-funds</link><description>贝莱德公司(BlackRock Inc.)计划推出两只货币市场基金，专为将现金存放在稳定币而非银行账户的投资者而设立，这表明这家全球最大的资产管理公司看到了数字美元经济中持久的客户群。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/il9lg0ZDzPqQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 21:18:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-08/blackrock-readies-launch-of-two-tokenized-money-market-funds</guid></item><item><title>Coinbase 陷入亏损，收入再次下降</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/coinbase-swings-to-a-loss-while-posting-another-revenue-drop</link><description>就在宣布大幅裁员和推动人工智能发展几天后，Coinbase Global Inc. 表明其财富与加密货币市场的联系有多么紧密。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iPgaPKxTDp9g/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 20:29:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/coinbase-swings-to-a-loss-while-posting-another-revenue-drop</guid></item><item><title>战略的比特币威胁隐藏着一个丑陋的真相</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-07/strategy-s-bitcoin-threat-hides-an-uglier-truth</link><description>数字资产国库正在寻求利润提升&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/is.35pDwYKdA/v8/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-07/strategy-s-bitcoin-threat-hides-an-uglier-truth</guid></item><item><title>币安称财政部已就交易所监管发出信函</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/binance-says-treasury-sent-letter-over-monitorship-of-exchange</link><description>据一位知情人士透露，近三年前，币安同意接受监管，同时承认美国对制裁和反洗钱违规行为的指控。币安收到了美国财政部的一封信，要求采访该加密货币交易所的员工并记录其记录，以调查潜在的制裁违规行为。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iJPv5.ht42Eg/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 18:04:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/binance-says-treasury-sent-letter-over-monitorship-of-exchange</guid></item><item><title>Kraken 母公司将以 6 亿美元收购 Reap Technologies</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/kraken-parent-to-buy-reap-for-600-million-in-asian-expansion</link><description>加密货币交易所 Kraken 的所有者已同意向 Reap Technologies 支付 6 亿美元，Reap Technologies 是一家面向稳定币的跨境和商业支付服务提供商。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i4rqC37VOMHg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 12:01:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/kraken-parent-to-buy-reap-for-600-million-in-asian-expansion</guid></item><item><title>Kalshi 在 Coatue 领投的一轮融资中获得 220 亿美元估值</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/kalshi-secures-22-billion-valuation-in-coatue-led-round</link><description>Kalshi Inc. 已完成一轮融资，该预测市场平台的估值达到 220 亿美元，大约是五个月前估值的两倍。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWtmvv51zsUQ/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 13:53:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-07/kalshi-secures-22-billion-valuation-in-coatue-led-round</guid></item></channel></rss>